<plot>B.O. Skunk finds himself attracted to various other animals, but one whiff and they run away. He tries some extreme techniques, including a 'Frank Sinatra' (qv) impersonation; that gets the stage mobbed, but they still run away. Finally, he tries camouflaging himself as a fox, only to meet and fall for another skunk disguised as a fox.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?337806</url></doc>
